<p class="short-reference" data-aid="154411303" id="short_reference1">&#x201C;August 12&#x2013;18. Alma 43&#x2013;52,&#x201D; <cite>Come, Follow Me&#x2014;For Home and Church: 2024</cite> (2023)</p>
