</a>
<figcaption>
<p data-aid="154410326" id="figure4_figure1_p1">&#x201C;Because of your diligence and your faith and your patience with the word in nourishing it, &#x2026; behold, by and by ye shall pluck the fruit thereof, which is most precious&#x201D; (<a class="scripture-ref" href="/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/32?lang=eng&amp;id=p42#p42">Alma 32:42</a>).</p>
</figcaption>
